{"questionId":"22064","questionHtml":"<p>show that, at the equilibrium point, the value of the mackerel population density is <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfrac><mi>δ</mi><mi>γ</mi></mfrac></math>;</p>","markschemeHtml":"<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>γ</mi><mi>M</mi><mi>S</mi><mo>-</mo><mi>δ</mi><mi>S</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></math>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p>since&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>S</mi><mo>≠</mo><mn>0</mn></math>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong>R1</strong></em></p>\n<p><br><strong>Note:</strong> Accept <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>S</mi><mo>&gt;</mo><mn>0</mn></math>.</p>\n<p><br>getting to given answer without further error by either cancelling or factorizing&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>M</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi>δ</mi><mi>γ</mi></mfrac></math>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong>AG</strong></em></p>\n<p><em><strong><br>[3 marks]</strong></em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"22064","referenceCode":"21M.3.AHL.TZ2.2b.i","subjectId":"51-dp-mathematics-applications-and-interpretation","title":"show that, at the equilibrium point, the value of the mackerel population density is δγ;","paper":"3","level":"AHL","questionNumber":"b.i","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 3]","breadcrumbLabels":["Topic 5—Calculus","Topic 5—Calculus","AHL 5.17—Phase portrait"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}}}